MuscleMag International - December 2013  USA

182 Pages | True PDF | English | 25 MB 


This magazine is devoted to both hardcore athletes and recreational bodybuilders who are looking for most-advanced training and nutritional advice available today. Designed for those who are serious about resistance training, and who are looking for a competitive edge to help them reach their goals in the fastest time possible.
